352
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:36,980
He already holds the highest position.

353
00:35:36,980 --> 00:35:42,920
He has no reason to brutally kill the emperors, let alone me.

354
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:49,120
But if someone is impersonating His Supreme Majesty with the Puppet Spell, it all makes sense.

