361
00:36:16,040 --> 00:36:20,620
Don't you think he is a lot like Huan Qin?

362
00:36:23,680 --> 00:36:25,640
The Golden Cicada's Wings were put in the Star Setter Pavilion.

363
00:36:25,640 --> 00:36:27,840
All these years, no one has ever found out about it.

